# Sky culture name
msgid "Sardinian"
msgstr ""

# Sky culture introduction section in markdown format
msgid ""
"Like all peoples of the world, even the ancient Sardinians, turned their "
"eyes to the sky that marked the time and the seasons. The peasant's world "
"has given its name to the stars and the constellations of the Sardinian "
"culture."
msgstr ""
"Comente totu sos populos de su mundu, fintzas sos sardos antigos, artziaiana "
"sos ogos a su chelu chi sinnaiat su tempus et sas istajones. Su mundu 'e su "
"sartu hat zau su numene a sos isteddos e a sas costellatziones de la cultura "
"sarda."

