# Sky culture authors section in markdown format
msgid ""
"These constellations have been created by the Stellarium's user *Giuseppe "
"Putzolu*, giuseppe.putzolu(at)gmail.com\n"
"\n"
"### Credits\n"
"\n"
"The constellations of the Sardinian culture are the result of research done "
"by Tonino Bussu and Marco Puddu"
msgstr ""
"Custas costellatziones sunu istatas criadas dae s'utilizadore de Stellarium "
"*Giuseppe Putzolu*, giuseppe.putzolu(at)gmail.com\n"
"\n"
"### Ringratziamentos\n"
"\n"
"Sas costellatziones de sa cultura sarda sun su frutu de sas ricercas fattas "
"dae Tonino Bussu et Marco Puddu"

